text:
the following serious issues are recurring and making me a number of visits to dealer and a multiple emails for the same.
1.While delivering the vehicle , the location of the vehicle has not been located and when I asked them , they said it will be fixed when I come for Number plate fixing.-  1 st visit
2.On the day of number plate fixing , they have done something and it worked only for 1 day and after that , only drive mode is working - 2nd visit
3.After I put so many mails to customer care and sadly response from customer care is very poor.Then technician from dealer called me for fixing the issue.I visited dealer and gave the vehicle for rectification.- 3rd visit
4.They have fixed techpack and the following issues are cropped up newly.
i)  Reverse mode on in display but vehicle not moving
ii) Vehicle has a vibration feel in the handle grip up to 22 Kmph speed after that OK
iii) In the traffic , it was very difficult to pick up from 15 KMph speed to the speed of following vehicle and they are shouting            to  move  forward.
iv) My vehicle always showing wrong location and most of the pick up a location while on driving and stayed there on;y.
v) Vehicle is always offline and rarely shows online.
vi ) Some times its not showing the charging status
vii) Trip details always faulty.The tech support team called me for trip details starting time and closing time and location.If , I provide these details , they will update in back end for showing trip details,This is not a good practice.The trip details has to pick up from geo location from GPS and trip to be updated automatically.Since a faulty GPS equipment along with other sensors  , the errors are recurring in my vehicle.
